                    </div>
                    <span>This is one of those rare books you'd treasure long after you have finished reading it. Chris Sells' writing style makes it easy to read and follow. His examples are concise and to the point and makes C# look simple and elegant. After reading the first few chapters I was very excited and I couldn't wait to get started on a project. Highly recommended.</span>
                  
              
